  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the ultimate retro video game store! where you sell video games, consoles, or rare collectibles, this game lets you live out your dream of running a thriving gaming business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/2ef99d68081bd2a36bd83842e043549b.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determine where products are displayed, manage your inventory, and keep track of popular trends and adjust to the ever-changing demand of the market. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/539c859012972d7f76bcf561e5b18fd2.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and personalize your own store, organize shelves and optimize for efficiency and aesthetics. Every detail is yours to customize, making your store truly one of a kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/bd3917805184bdc9872224d13aa0f8c1.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reinvest your hard-earned profits to take your shop to the next level! Expand your store, License new game systems, and hire more staff to become the best game store in town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the ultimate retro video game store! where you sell video games, consoles, or rare collectibles, this game lets you live out your dream of running a thriving gaming business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/2ef99d68081bd2a36bd83842e043549b.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Determine where products are displayed, manage your inventory, and keep track of popular trends and adjust to the ever-changing demand of the market. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/0bd47e87e818975d0610082cd4457987.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/539c859012972d7f76bcf561e5b18fd2.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design and personalize your own store, organize shelves and optimize for efficiency and aesthetics. Every detail is yours to customize, making your store truly one of a kind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/5805f795f6ff69753c5d5c1666c6c78a.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/bd3917805184bdc9872224d13aa0f8c1.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reinvest your hard-earned profits to take your shop to the next level! Expand your store, License new game systems, and hire more staff to become the best game store in town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.poster.avif?t=1744717347\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.webm?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3392280/extras/f94302c0a2e56ef13cbda2dfa9cf935e.mp4?t=1744717347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
